❖ AC, DR, AR, PC, MAR, MBR, IR

📋 TABLE 6: CPU Registers and Applications

| Sr No | Name                    | Symbol | Description                                                    |
| ----- | ----------------------- | ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| 1     | Accumulator             | AC     | Stores information taken from memory                           |
| 2     | Data Register           | DR     | Holds memory operand                                           |
| 3     | Address Register        | AR     | Holds address for memory                                       |
